<h2 id="research">Research</h2>
<p>The NHS header was updated in September 2023. It includes exposed navigation links and a drop down that says "More" instead of a menu button. The search box now fills the width of the screen on mobile.</p>
<p>On the NHS website, we found that exposing main topics helps users navigate and find what they're looking for. The dynamic resizing and the "More" button help users on mobile navigate top tasks.</p> 
